  <li><a href="Control.html">Control Structures </a>
    <ul>
      <li>Relational Operators - &gt;,&lt;,&gt;=,&lt;=,= =, ~ = </li>
      <li>Logical Operators - &amp;, |, ~ for AND, OR, NOT </li>
